ZH: 潮流是一个很有意思的话题。
EN: Fashion is an interesting topic.
ZH: 她总是跟上最新的潮流。
EN: She always keeps up with the latest trends.
ZH: 这种服装款式非常符合潮流。
EN: This clothing style is very fashionable.
ZH: 潮流啊，总是变来变去。
EN: Trends always come and go.
ZH: 这个品牌所推崇的就是个性和潮流。
EN: The brand values individuality and fashion trends.
ZH: 在这座城市，你能感受到潮流的脉搏。
EN: In this city, you can feel the pulse of fashion.
ZH: 总是希望自己走在时尚潮流的前沿。
EN: Always wanting to be at the forefront of fashion trends.
ZH: 潮流博主推荐的产品总是很受欢迎。
EN: Products recommended by fashion bloggers are always popular.
ZH: 这个鞋子跟不上潮流了。
EN: These shoes are no longer in fashion.
ZH: 她的穿着总是很符合潮流趋势。
EN: She always dresses according to the latest fashion trends.
ZH: 潮流始终是年轻人关注的焦点。
EN: Fashion trends are always the focus of young people.
ZH: 他是这个国家时尚潮流的代表。
EN: He is a representative of the fashion trends in this country.
ZH: 潮流有时候影响了年轻人的价值观。
EN: Fashion trends sometimes influence the values of young people.
ZH: 这个品牌的风格与当代潮流相契合。
EN: The style of this brand aligns with contemporary fashion trends.
ZH: 潮流通常是由名人和设计师引领。
EN: Fashion trends are usually led by celebrities and designers.
ZH: 随着时间的推移，潮流会发生变化。
EN: Fashion trends change over time.
ZH: 潮流展示了不同的审美观念。
EN: Fashion showcases different aesthetic concepts.
ZH: 这个品牌没有追随潮流，它有自己的风格。
EN: This brand doesn't follow fashion trends; it has its own style.
ZH: 潮流的变化让人难以预测。
EN: The changes in fashion trends are unpredictable.
ZH: 她总能穿出独特的潮流风格。
EN: She always wears a unique fashion style.
